{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>OBSCURA</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the mysterious atmosphere of Obscura, a first-person investigative game where you play as a medium determined to solve unsolved cases.<br>Explore places haunted by tragic events and uncover the secrets buried in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore the invisible, reveal the truth.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a medium, your unique gift allows you to communicate with spirits and discover fragments of the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Search an abandoned apartment, observe the smallest details, and collect objects linked to past tragedies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each clue brings you closer to the truth, but be warned, some truths are darker than they appear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rituals to reveal the unspeakable.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect items marked by the past and use mysterious rituals to uncover buried memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine the right ritual fragments to trigger visions and reconstruct crime scenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each revelation will guide you toward solving the case.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you be ready to face the buried truths of Obscura?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398370/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736924207","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398370/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736924207","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398370/6dab8b39572fff3ef6c45e441a859d11e7ffe43